(173, 'Explorer\'s Guide to the Semantic Web', 1932394206, 304, '2004-06-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/passin.jpg', 'A complex set of extensions to the World Wide Web, the Semantic Web will make data and services more accessible to computers and useful to people. Some of these extensions are being deployed, and many are coming in the next years. This is the only book to', '\"A thorough look at one vision of the Web\'s future ...particularly well written...Highly recommended.\" -- Choice Magazine', 'PUBLISH'),
(174, 'Practical LotusScript', 1884777767, 512, '1999-05-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/patton.jpg', 'Practical LotusScript covers the LotusScript programming language like no other book on the market. It starts with the core languge and proceeds to cover the specifics of Lotus Notes in complete detail. Advanced topics include report generation, working w', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(175, 'Domino Development with Java', 1930110049, 467, '2000-08-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/patton2.jpg', 'Domino Development with Java takes the mysteries out of using the Java programming language within the Domino development environment. It provides a solid foundation for working utilization of the Java programming language in the Domino Application Server', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(176, 'Windows PowerShell in Action', 1932394907, 576, '2007-02-01 08:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/payette.jpg', 'Windows has an easy-to-use interface, but if you want to automate it, life can get hard. That is, unless you use PowerShell, an elegant new dynamic language from Microsoft designed as an all-purpose Windows scripting tool. PowerShell lets you script admin', '   If all it had going for it was the authoratative pedigree of the writer, it might be worth it, but it\'s also well-written, well-organized, and thorough, which I think makes it invaluable as both a learning tool and a reference.       Slashdot.org', 'PUBLISH'),
(177, 'Windows PowerShell in Action, Second Edition', 1935182137, 700, '2011-05-15 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/payette2.jpg', 'Windows PowerShell transformed the way administrators and developers interact with Windows. PowerShell, an elegant dynamic language from Microsoft, lets you script administrative tasks and control Windows from the command line. Because it\'s a full-feature', 'Windows PowerShell in Action, Second Edition is a completely revised edition of the best selling book on PowerShell, written by Bruce Payette, one of the founding members of the Windows PowerShell team, co-designer of the PowerShell language, and the prin', 'PUBLISH'),
(178, 'Silverlight 4 in Action, Revised Edition', 1935182374, 425, '2010-10-04 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/pbrown.jpg', 'Anyone who has gotten a taste of what it can do knows that Silverlight represents an entirely new level of rich web interface technology for Microsoft developers. With Silverlight, developers can use JavaScript, C#, and other languages to build user-frien', 'Silverlight in Action, Revised Edition is a comprehensive guide to Silverlight, taking you from Hello World through the techniques you\'ll need to build sophisticated rich web apps. This new edition covers all the new features added in the latest versions ', 'PUBLISH'),
(179, 'Silverlight 5 in Action', 1617290319, 925, '2012-06-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/pbrown2.jpg', '', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(180, 'Hibernate Quickly', 1932394419, 456, '2005-08-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/peak.jpg', 'Positioned as a layer between the application and the database, Hibernate is a powerful object/relational persistence and query service for Java. It takes care of automating a tedious task: the manual bridging of the gap between object oriented code and t', '\"If you want to learn Hibernate quickly, this book shows you step by step.\" - Sang Shin, Java Technology Architect, Sun Microsystems', 'PUBLISH'),
(181, 'Generative Art', 1935182625, 0, '2011-06-30 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/pearson.jpg', '', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(182, 'Windows Phone 7 in Action', 1617290092, 0, '2012-08-21 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/perga.jpg', 'Windows Phone 7 is a major shift in the way Microsoft developers design, develop, and sell mobile apps. By leveraging a trio of established technologies-Silverlight, XNA, and C#   developers can blend what they already know about Windows development with ', 'Windows Phone 7 in Action is a hands-on guide to building mobile applications for WP7 using Silverlight, C#, and XNA. Written for developers who already know their way around Visual Studio, this book zips through the basics, such as writing code to dial t', 'PUBLISH'),
(183, 'Lift in Action', 1935182803, 450, '2011-11-18 08:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/perrett.jpg', '', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(184, 'Web Development with Apache and Perl', 1930110065, 424, '2002-04-01 08:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/petersen.jpg', 'Open source tools provide a powerful and flexible environment for web development and maintenance. If your site has complex business rules or server logic, then you need more than just an interface builder. You need a strong application language with effe', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(185, 'Real-World Functional Programming', 1933988924, 560, '2009-12-01 08:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/petricek.jpg', 'Functional programming languages are good at expressing complex ideas in a succinct, declarative way. Functional concepts such as \"immutability\" and \"function values\" make it easier to reason about code   as well as helping with concurrency. The new F# la', 'This book teaches the ideas and techniques of functional programming applied to real-world problems. You\'ll see how the functional way of thinking changes the game for .NET developers. Then, you\'ll tackle common issues using a functional approach. The boo', 'PUBLISH'),
(186, 'Machine Learning in Action', 1617290181, 0, '2012-04-04 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/pharrington.jpg', 'It\'s been said that data is the new \"dirt\"   the raw material from which and on which you build the structures of the modern world. And like dirt, data can seem like a limitless, undifferentiated mass. The ability to take raw data, access it, filter it, p', 'Machine Learning in Action is a unique book that blends the foundational theories of machine learning with the practical realities of building tools for everyday data analysis. In it, you\'ll use the flexible Python programming language to build programs t', 'PUBLISH'),
(187, 'Dependency Injection', 193398855, 352, '2009-08-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/prasanna.jpg', 'In object-oriented programming, a central program normally controls other objects in a module, library, or framework. With dependency injection, this pattern is inverted   a reference to a service is placed directly into the object which eases testing and', '   If you do large scale java apps, you probably want to have someone on the team have this book.       Michael Neale', 'PUBLISH'),
(188, 'Understanding Enterprise SOA', 1932394591, 280, '2005-11-01 08:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/pulier.jpg', 'Understanding Enterprise SOA gives technologists and business people an invaluable and until now missing integrated picture of the issues and their interdependencies. You will learn how to think in a big way, moving confidently between technology- and bus', '\"SOA is real ... Pulier is uniquely qualified to make [it] accessible to the general business audience.\" - Paul Gaffney, Staples, Inc., From the Foreword', 'PUBLISH'),
(189, 'Open-Source ESBs in Action', 1933988215, 528, '2008-09-01 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/rademakers.jpg', 'The need for enterprise integration is widespread for the simple reason that businesses require independent applications to exchange information with each other. A CRM application must know about the order history of a customer, but that history is stored', '', 'PUBLISH'),
(190, 'Activiti in Action', 1617290122, 0, '2012-07-12 07:00:00', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/AKIAJC5RLADLUMVRPFDQ.book-thumb-images/rademakers2.jpg', '', '', 'PUBLISH');
